<section class="replica-timeline" aria-label="Conversation timeline">
  <article class="timeline-row">
    <span class="timeline-avatar assistant">C</span>
    <div class="timeline-bubble">
      <p><strong>Codex</strong> updated the hero to emphasize multi-provider orchestration and BYOS.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="timeline-row">
    <span class="timeline-avatar user">U</span>
    <div class="timeline-bubble">
      <p>This mockup does not align with our app. We need a true 1:1 replica.</p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <article class="timeline-row">
    <span class="timeline-avatar assistant">C</span>
    <div class="timeline-bubble">
      <p>Rebuilding from web primitives: sidebar, top bar, timeline, and composer.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>

<style>
  .replica-timeline {
    display: grid;
    gap: 10px;
    align-content: start;
    padding: 14px;
    flex: 1;
    min-height: 0;
  }

  .timeline-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 33px minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .timeline-avatar {
    width: 33px;
    height: 33px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #dce7ff;
    background: #2b6fd6;
  }

  .timeline-avatar.user {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
  }

  .timeline-bubble {
    border: 1px solid var(--replica-border);
    background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.095), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08));
    border-radius: 18px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
  }

  .timeline-bubble p {
    margin: 0;
    color: rgba(236, 236, 236, 0.9);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.35;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
</style>
